_sText:
This is my first beta for de_reclaim.

Industrial setting in a water reclamation plant. There are two bio-hazardous tank sites, the terrorist's job is to destroy these.

My plan with this map is to not stop prematurely. I want this map to go all the way to professional status, radar, sprites, area portals, the works. So by releasing this, I just want to know feedback; ie. opinions of aesthetics, gameplay feedback, stuff along those lines.

Hope you enjoy!

fishy (bmx3r1011)


www.intoxgaming.com
